   "metadata": {},
   "source": [

   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "id": "3217a63f-6550-4076-a380-50fc533b7ea7",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "load experiment[Dataset2] in dataset[Dataset2_MS_raw] from /home/yzy/anaconda3/envs/SODB/lib/python3.9/site-packages/pysodb-1.0.0-py3.9.egg/ysodb/cache/Dataset2_MS_raw/Dataset2.h5ad\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "import pysodb\n",
    "sodb = pysodb.SODB()\n",
    "adata_dict = sodb.load_dataset('Dataset2_MS_raw')\n",
    "adata = list(adata_dict.values())[0]"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "id": "98647931-5637-48ae-b2d3-b82df01c3488",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "data size: (2042, 79)\n"
     ]
    }

   "source": [
    "print('data size:',adata.shape)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "40119507-3b12-4025-8625-fc29be8cb7ae",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## cell type clustering"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "id": "a9c24c28-5136-4f60-b33f-6d2ae85c4cc8",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "sc.pp.highly_variable_genes(adata, flavor=\"seurat_v3\", n_top_genes=4000)\n",
    "sc.pp.normalize_total(adata, inplace=True)\n",
    "sc.pp.log1p(adata)\n",
    "sc.pp.pca(adata)\n",
    "sc.pp.neighbors(adata)\n",
    "sc.tl.leiden(adata,resolution=2,key_added='ct')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "3d071bbe-48cb-4fa7-ad5d-0d71ac6625cd",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "##  MS"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "id": "193e8a7c-08ce-4f07-9e40-6c242ea01a83",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# initialize the MS object\n",
    "ms = MS.MS(\n",
    "    adata\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "# set the number of scales, default is 15\n",
    "ms.set_MS_para(\n",
    "    n_scales=15\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "# construct the context-aware representation\n",
    "ms.k_representation_mp()\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 7,
   "id": "2d0f943c-91ed-40dd-8c46-d464b84c4157",
   "metadata": {},

    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "searching resolution to k=6\n",
      "Res =  0.1 Num of clusters =  4\n",
      "Res =  0.2 Num of clusters =  5\n",
      "Res changed to 0.2\n",
      "Res =  0.30000000000000004 Num of clusters =  6\n",
      "recommended res =  0.30000000000000004\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "# identify tissue structure given the number of k\n",
    "k_expected = len(adata.obs['gt'].cat.categories)\n",
    "ms.run_clustering_normal(\n",
    "    k_expected \n",
    "    # the clustering parameter\n",
    "    # positive value for the number of clusters\n",
    "    # negative value for the clustering resolution\n",
    ")"
   ]
  },
